General.Name: Tangiamo Touch Technology AB
General.Description: Tangiamo Touch Technology AB (publ) provides multiplayer electronic gaming machines and visual identification software products. It offers MultiPLAY, a touch table gaming platform that provides the live roulette gaming experience to players; dice shakers solution with automated dice recognition technology for dice games; TNG Slot platform, which offers up to 5 players to play together on one slot machine; and Gaming bridge, a casino system that expand gaming tables with remote gaming on tablets and online. The company was formerly known as TouchTable AB and changed its name to Tangiamo Touch Technology AB in April 2010. Tangiamo Touch Technology AB (publ) was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
